{"tid":2478721,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"傳GRAB透過SPAC於美國上市 （1）","createTime":"2021-04-07T09:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T13:47:10.000Z","uid":17569,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"dc094fcd9a234cde4710c39cc0de003cf8f2b4d7","tid":2478721,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:23:55.000Z","msg":"Singapore&rsquo;s Grab set to list in New York in biggest Spac merger<br />\n<br />\nGrab, south-east Asia&rsquo;s most valuable start-up, is set for the largest merger between a private business and a blank-cheque vehicle in a deal that will value the SoftBank-backed technology group at about $35bn. <br />\n<br />\nSingapore-based Grab, whose offerings include ride-hailing and financial services, could finalise an agreement to list in New York via one of Altimeter Capital&rsquo;s special purpose acquisition companies as soon as this week, according to three people with direct knowledge of the situation.<br />\n<br />\nThe merger would be with one of the US investment firm&rsquo;s two Altimeter Growth Spacs and would come after Grab&rsquo;s board agreed to a preliminary deal last month.<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://amp.ft.com/content/73d8b26c-3d61-48ec-8027-25c4cd625488\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F73d8b26c-3d61-48ec-8027-25c4cd625488&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtEYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=2ac3b8ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://amp.ft.com/content/73d8b26c-3d61-48ec-8027-25c4cd625488</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信大家去過東南亞國家旅遊<br />\n都知GRAB係幾咁common<br />\n可以話係東南亞市場中嘅Uber<br />\n唔清楚可以自己Google下<br />\n<br />\n有傳佢將會透過Altimeter SPACs合併上市<br />\n而家隻SPAC市值8億<br />\n相信合併成功後估價遠超呢個價<br />\n消息指最快今個星期內有結果<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Altimeter 有兩隻SPAC<br />\nSPAC: AGC 同 AGCB<br />\n大家都估AGC係正選</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbW5jVPtj9jVQ8UNz552NFJx3D55NUB1GVVfnyhnxQVMn?filename=mrQDs3J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmrQDs3J.jpg&h=c7e1e2c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUXFRffFZmxAdEcnuTbeE8YtFufcb2sw7wWMPtjwqrTut?filename=t3TtQgK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3TtQgK.png&h=0af69edb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>投資涉及風險，大家投資與否都應做足功課<br />\n衡量好自己風險 <br />\n一切都未成事 比較高風險<br />\n唔建議大家賭身家</strong>"},{"pid":"370036ac99e434bbb8b7d7f4a1c745d1168360dc","tid":2478721,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:26:45.000Z","msg":"大家可以交流下<br />\n第一次開post講股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：持有1100股"},{"pid":"da38f945aa5427ea6d7d8450dbcf92b82dbe6c0c","tid":2478721,"uid":130365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:29:50.000Z","msg":"原來GRAB係Singapore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前係泰國見周圍都係Grab 又平到仆街, 以為係泰國公司"},{"pid":"bc62a69bfa1763d536c1f73f864f4e948b662d70","tid":2478721,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da38f945aa5427ea6d7d8450dbcf92b82dbe6c0c","tid":2478721,"uid":130365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:29:50.000Z","msg":"原來GRAB係Singapore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前係泰國見周圍都係Grab 又平到仆街, 以為係泰國公司"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:32:45.000Z","msg":"佢總部係喺新加坡<br />\n但創辦人係兩個Malaysian"},{"pid":"e2451e898b9940668f36bb3ecf46df8304f28c9f","tid":2478721,"uid":167163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"370036ac99e434bbb8b7d7f4a1c745d1168360dc","tid":2478721,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:26:45.000Z","msg":"大家可以交流下<br />\n第一次開post講股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：持有